http://www.cyberciti.biz/faq/how-to-find-gateway-ip-address/

To identify your public ip address,do one of these:

curl ident.me

curl ifconfig.me

curl tnx.nl/ip

curl icanhazip.com

curl ipecho.net/plain

curl ip.appspot.com

curl whatsmyip.akamai.com
